	* config/: Makefile.am, tgr2shppoly_2006.dbfawk: Add a new DBFAWK
	  file for the 2006 TIGER/Line data.

	  This data has "UACU" and "URCU" fields instead of the RS_A15 and
	  RS_A16 fields that older TIGER/Line data had.

