	* WMSRadar.geo, src/map_WMS.c: Moving the VERSION tag into the .geo
	  file.  Some servers are picky about this, so it can't be
	  hard-coded.

2005-05-24 12:49  we7u

	* src/map_WMS.c: Adding/changing some comments.

